ScaffoldWithConfirmation
========================
Extended version of scaffolds.
This scaffold has a confirmation page.


Usage
=====

1. Install plugin.

  rails plugin install git://github.com/usualoma/scaffold_with_confirmation.git

2. Generate model.

  rails generate ModelName [ field:type ... ]


Example
=======

  rails generate scaffold post
  rails generate scaffold post title:string body:text published:boolean
  rails generate scaffold purchase order_id:integer amount:decimal


